！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">追究警方暴行！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">追究警方暴行！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">落實真雙普選！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">落實真雙普選！</span><br />\nloop from 光復香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他口號大家都可以提出， 但個人唔希望再叫香港人加油，冇實際作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n希慎手足約個時間一齊叫好唔好"},{"pid":"1d72769a0cc1d9ef10c3eced996e3e1efd3a4080","tid":1482831,"uid":53349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"播歌都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da01bb622b8160e3197d4cc7cab82aff26c67611","tid":1482831,"uid":159596,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"屌啫 無話割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n批評兩句就話割<br />\n已經特登開個po響創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110440e58b33f07084aab035a29a6933e930cb4d","tid":1482831,"uid":14262,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"af724825c84ed2185a145a028ca08eff6b66f6c9","tid":1482831,"uid":107060,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"75b6ab9f65a4653e69c677fe70e09d53dad17eff","tid":1482831,"uid":14262,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"不如唔好再叫兄弟各自爬山，反正做咩都屌都分化。<br />\n<br />\n勇武行為又屌，到和理非又屌<br />\n<br />\n仲學人講爬山論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"遊行氣氛本來就係沈重<br />\n係咪下下少少批評都要話人分化咁玻璃心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:29:15.000Z","msg":"相信和平抗爭嘅人,相信公民抗命嘅人,繼續公民抗命。相信佔馬路,相信絕食,相信罷交稅...等等唔同和平手段嘅人繼續去做。我鼓勵你地去做,我希望你地去做。我唔希望因為有人批評你地嘅手段,結果就完全放棄你地相信嘅野。同時間相信勇武抗爭嘅人,一樣都要繼續做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記得槍口對外就得</span>，屌同路人有咩意思，比意見都唔係咁既態度比，明唔明，我都唔同意播歌。"},{"pid":"f2f24a7be7bf5236b68d2b95845fb45f167d10e6","tid":1482831,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a2d671f335e579353ce158673067ca3a9a93dd12","t